description:
What do you see? What do you feel? Maybe you see an oil spill, a landscape full of candy, or simply nothing at all. Maybe you feel a sense of nostalgia, or calmness instead. For me, that's the beauty of this piece and abstract art altogether - everyone will have a different interpretation that evokes completely unique emotions, thoughts and memories for every individual. 

///

'Warm Evenings in the Garden' is my first ever 1/1 artwork minted via blockchain technology. Sourcing colour and texture from a digitised, distorted version of an original acrylic painting, the piece contains hundreds of fragmented and expressive digital brush strokes.

///

4000x5000
